        "text_snippet": "The solvent-free direct HDO of 5,5′-(furan-2-ylmethylene)bis(2-methylfuran) (i.e. 1a in Scheme 1) was conducted under solvent-free conditions in a fixed bed... Over the Ni/H-ZSM-5-EG catalyst, 1a was almost totally converted to alkanes (carbon yield 93.7%).",
